#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.exponential"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from an exponential distribution."
msgstr "从指数分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:3 of
msgid "Its probability density function is"
msgstr "其概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"f(x; \\frac{1}{\\beta}) = \\frac{1}{\\beta} \\exp(-\\frac{x}{\\beta}),\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:7 of
msgid ""
"for ``x > 0`` and 0 elsewhere. :math:`\\beta` is the scale parameter, "
"which is the inverse of the rate parameter :math:`\\lambda = 1/\\beta`. "
"The rate parameter is an alternative, widely used parameterization of the"
" exponential distribution [3]_."
msgstr ""
"对于 ``x > 0`` 为上述公式，其余地方为 0。:math:`\\beta` 是尺度参数，即"
"速率参数 :math:`\\lambda = 1/\\beta` 的倒数。速率参数是指数分布的一种替代"
"且广泛使用的参数化方式 [3]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:12 of
msgid ""
"The exponential distribution is a continuous analogue of the geometric "
"distribution.  It describes many common situations, such as the size of "
"raindrops measured over many rainstorms [1]_, or the time between page "
"requests to Wikipedia [2]_."
msgstr ""
"指数分布是几何分布的连续类比。它描述了许多常见情况，例如多次暴雨中测量的"
"雨滴大小 [1]_，或 Wikipedia 页面请求之间的时间间隔 [2]_。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:17 of
msgid "The scale parameter, :math:`\\beta = 1/\\lambda`."
msgstr "尺度参数，:math:`\\beta = 1/\\lambda`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:19 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``scale`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``np.array(scale).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），当 ``scale`` 为标量时返回单个值。否则，"
"抽取 ``np.array(scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:24 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:26 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True 则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:28 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:31 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized exponential distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的指数分布中抽取的样本。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:36 of
msgid ""
"Peyton Z. Peebles Jr., \"Probability, Random Variables and Random Signal "
"Principles\", 4th ed, 2001, p. 57."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:38 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Poisson process\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_process"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.exponential.exponential:40 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Exponential distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponential_distribution"
msgstr ""

